		<h2>When to Move On</h2>
		<p>If you haven't conceived after 3-6 cycles of oral medications with or without IUI, your doctor may recommend:</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Switching medications</li>
			<li>Adding injectable medications</li>
			<li>Moving to IVF</li>
			<li>Additional testing</li>
		</ul>

